***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Grafana Configuration
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Admin credentials (CHANGE THESE for production!)
***REMOVED*** Generate password with: openssl rand -base64 24
GF_SECURITY_ADMIN_USER=admin
GF_SECURITY_ADMIN_PASSWORD=CHANGE_ME_GRAFANA_PASSWORD

***REMOVED*** Disable anonymous access for production
GF_AUTH_ANONYMOUS_ENABLED=false
GF_AUTH_ANONYMOUS_ORG_ROLE=Viewer
GF_AUTH_DISABLE_LOGIN_FORM=false

***REMOVED*** Server URL (adjust if exposing externally)
***REMOVED*** LAN access: http://192.168.x.x:3000
GF_SERVER_ROOT_URL=http://localhost:3000

***REMOVED*** Disable telemetry
GF_ANALYTICS_REPORTING_ENABLED=false
GF_ANALYTICS_CHECK_FOR_UPDATES=false

***REMOVED*** Enable TraceQL editor for Tempo
GF_FEATURE_TOGGLES_ENABLE=traceqlEditor

***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Data Retention (adjust based on NAS storage capacity)
***REMOVED*** -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
***REMOVED*** Loki (logs) - default 14 days
***REMOVED*** LOKI_RETENTION_PERIOD=336h

***REMOVED*** Tempo (traces) - default 7 days
***REMOVED*** TEMPO_RETENTION_PERIOD=168h

***REMOVED*** Mimir (metrics) - default 15 days
***REMOVED*** MIMIR_RETENTION_PERIOD=15d

